      "description": "To complete track improvement work, the Greenbush, Kingston, and Fall River/New Bedford Lines will originate and terminate at Braintree during the following weekends:\r\n\u2022 April 11-2, 18-19, & 25-26\r\n\u2022 May 9-10\r\n\r\nPassengers can use the Red Line for service between South Station and Braintree. Inbound Greenbush Line trains will terminate at Braintree after stopping at Weymouth Landing/East Braintree, a journey of approximately 9 minutes. Outbound Greenbush Line trains will originate at Braintree approximately 10 minutes prior to the schedule Weymouth Landing/East Braintree departure time.\r\n\r\nAffected stations:\r\nSouth Station\r\nJFK/UMass\r\nQuincy Center\r\nBraintree",
