      "title": "",
      "description": "\u2022 Local and express shuttle buses will be available\r\n\r\n\u2022 This is to accommodate signal improvement work.\r\n\r\n\u2022 A diversion schedule will be in effect.\r\n\r\n\u2022 An express shuttle will operate nonstop between North Station and Anderson/Woburn.\r\n\r\n\u2022 A local shuttle will operate between North Station and Anderson/Woburn, making all local stops.\r\n\r\n\u2022 Riders using the shuttle buses should budget extra travel time. For example, a rider traveling to North Station from Anderson/Woburn should budget up to 15 minutes additional travel on the express shuttle and up to 40 minutes additional travel on the local shuttle.\r\n\r\nShuttle bus pick up/drop off locations:\r\n\r\nNorth Station:\r\nNashua St @ Red Auerbach Way\r\n\r\nWest Medford:\r\nInbound \u2013 High St @ Canal St (MBTA Routes 94, 95, & 326 bus stop)\r\nOutbound \u2013 High St @ Warren St (MBTA Routes 94, 95, & 326 bus stop)\r\n\r\nWedgemere:\r\nWedgemere Station Parking Lot (inbound side)\r\n\r\nWinchester Center:\r\nLaraway Rd @ Winchester Center Station (MBTA Route 134 bus stop)\r\n\r\nAnderson/Woburn:\r\nAnderson/Woburn Station Busway (adjacent to Logan Express bus stop)",
